CPU: 4 cores

1Ô∏è‚É£ Icarus Verilog (iverilog)

Purpose:
Icarus Verilog is an open-source Verilog simulator. It is used to compile and simulate Verilog HDL code.

Installation:

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install iverilog

Check installation:

iverilog -v

